Title: Nose Ring DIAMOND Cut 14 ga Sterling Silver Hoop Cartilage SPARKLE Tragus Helix
Description: This Nose Ring is AWESOME, UNIQUE, AND DAZZLING!!! WE LOVE THESE!!! Basically, this ring is great for someone who wants a little bit of sparkle on their nose or ear...and who doesn't? :) 1 (one) Nose Ring /Cuff -TINY Small Diamond style cut seeing silver Hoop Earrings Pierced or Non Pierced, Cartilage, or helix.
